{"article_id":"TqJuKS4f1BXNg0s9","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"EL PASO , Texas","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"( ) -","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"Potential White House hopeful Beto O ' Rourke accused Donald Trump of fear-mongering on Monday","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"and the Republican president mocked the Democrat as a \" young man","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"who lost \" in dueling rallies","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"that could preview the tenor of the 2020 election campaign .","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"O ' Rourke ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"who narrowly lost his 2018 bid for a U.S. Senate seat ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"accused Trump of stoking \" false fear \" about immigrants and telling \" lies \" about his hometown El Paso ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"which","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"Trump said","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"was a dangerous place","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"before it had a border fence .","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"\" We stand for America","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"and we stand against a wall , \"","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"O ' Rourke told a crowd of several thousand supporters , many","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"waving \" Beto 2020 \" signs and wearing \" Immigrants Make America Great \" baseball caps .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"\" Walls do not save lives ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"they end lives . \"","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Two hundred yards away in El Paso County Coliseum , Trump told his supporters","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"that O ' Rourke had \" little going for himself ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"although he ' s got a great first name . \"","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"\" We are all challenged by a young man","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"who lost an election to","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"( Republican Senator )","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"Ted Cruz , \"","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"said Trump .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"that O ' Rourke ' s rally was smaller than his ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"and that was a bad sign :","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"\" That may be the end of his presidential bid . \"","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"could not verify Trump ' s claim","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"that 35,000 people attended his rally , with about 10,000 inside .","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"The city ' s fire department allowed only the capacity 6,500 inside ,","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"the El Paso Times reported .","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"Police estimated","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"between 10,000 and 15,000 attended the O ' Rourke march and rally ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"the newspaper said .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"As the two men spoke ,","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"U.S. congressional negotiators said","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"they had reached a tentative deal","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"to try to avert another partial government shutdown .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Aides said","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"it did not contain the $ 5.7 billion","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"Trump wanted for his wall","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"that triggered the shutdown last month .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Trump made clear on Monday","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"he would not drop the demand for a border wall","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"that delights his followers ,","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"first made in his campaign in the 2016 election .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"Giant banners at his rally read","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"\" Finish The Wall . \"","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"Beto O'Rourke , the Democratic former Texas congressman , addresses supporters before an anti-Trump march in El Paso , Texas , U.S. , February 11 , 2019 .","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"/Loren Elliott","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"National polls show","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"the wall is not popular with the majority of voters .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"A /IPSOS survey found","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"43 percent of the U.S. public supported additional border fencing .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"Trump said","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"he had heard about a possible deal in Washington","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"before he took the stage ,","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"but added :","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"\" Just so you know -","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"we ' re building the wall anyway .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Maybe progress has been made -","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"maybe not . \"","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"It was Trump ' s first direct clash with a potential 2020 rival , albeit on separate stages .","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"O ' Rourke relished the prime-time national platform ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"sometimes breaking into Spanish ,","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"in what sounded like a campaign speech .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"He decried the Trump administration ' s separation of immigrant children from their parents at the border .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"Dreamers","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"- undocumented people","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"brought to the United States by their parents","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"when they were children -","depth":15},{"id":76,"text":"should be given citizenship , and their parents a pathway to citizenship .","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"\" With a president","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"who describes Mexican immigrants as rapists and criminals ,","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"we have a chance","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"to tell him and the country","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"that immigrants commit crime at a lower rate than Americans","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"who are born in this country , \"","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"he said to shouts of \" Beto , Beto . \"","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"Trump was pressing his case on immigration in the Democratic bastion of El Paso county ,","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"where the population is over 80 percent Hispanic .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"\" I will never sign a bill","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"that forces the mass release of violent criminals into our country , \"","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"he said ,","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"referring to a Democratic proposal in the Washington talks","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"to lower the cap on detentions of criminal aliens by Immigration and Customs Enforcement","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"( ICE ) .","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"Under Monday ' s tentative agreement , the cap would likely stay around the same as in previous years ,","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"a congressional aide said .","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"Although O ' Rourke ' s full-throated denunciation of the president sounded like he planned to run against Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"the two-time congressman declined to discuss a potential bid","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"when asked by reporters on a conference call on Monday .","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"O ' Rourke told Oprah Winfrey last week","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"he would make a final decision","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"about running for president","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"by the end of the month .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":201,"left":0,"right":200,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":200,"left":1,"right":199,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":199,"left":150,"right":198,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":136,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":117,"right":135,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":111,"right":116,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":104,"right":110,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":2,"right":103,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":103,"left":3,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","n